<section>

	<article class='post' id="post-477178" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Article">

		<h1 id="headline" itemprop="url headline name">Once You Use Bitcoin You Can&#8217;t Go &#8216;Back&#8217; &mdash; And That&#8217;s Its Fatal Flaw</h1>
<link itemprop="url" href="http://www.wired.com/2013/11/once-you-use-bitcoin-you-cant-go-back-and-that-irreversibility-is-its-fatal-flaw/" />
<link itemprop="image" href="http://www.wired.com/wp-content/uploads/images_blogs/opinion/2013/11/bitcoin-phone-comp.jpg" />

<ul class="entry-header">
	
	<li class="author">By&nbsp;<a rel="author" href="http://www.wired.com/author/morphizm/">Scott Thill</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;</li>

	<li class="entryDate"><time itemprop="datePublished" datetime="2013-11-26T09:27:36+00:00">11.26.13</time>&nbsp;&nbsp;&#124;&nbsp;&nbsp;</li>
	<li class="entryTime">9:27 am&nbsp;&nbsp;&#124;&nbsp;&nbsp;</li>

		<li><a href="http://www.wired.com/2013/11/once-you-use-bitcoin-you-cant-go-back-and-that-irreversibility-is-its-fatal-flaw/" rel="bookmark" title="Once You Use Bitcoin You Can&#8217;t Go &#8216;Back&#8217; &mdash; And That&#8217;s Its Fatal Flaw">Permalink</a></li></ul> <!-- /#authors entry-header  -->


<ul id='social-top' class="social-bookmarking-module ">
            <li class="facebook-small">
            <div class="facebook-share-button"><a href="https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.wired.com%2F2013%2F11%2Fonce-you-use-bitcoin-you-cant-go-back-and-that-irreversibility-is-its-fatal-flaw%2F" target="_blank" class="indent">Share on Facebook</a><!-- i have a purpose! i am the counter! delete me at your own peril! --><div>0</div></div>        </li>
